      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.0394450905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私、走ってて、苦しくて……足が重くて……\n転んで、痛くて……何度も立ち止まりそうになって……",
      "startTime": 123.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "その度にキツネさんを強く握り締めてきたんです\nそうすれば、{user}さんや……",
